OL,3,CCouncil tax burden almost doubles for
OL,4,Cpoorest households
OL,6,FWords by Angus Neale, ITV Peston
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FCouncil tax consumes 4.8 per cent of
OL,10,Fincome for the poorest households,
OL,11,Faccording to research by the
OL,12,FResolution Foundation. This is more
OL,13,Fthan triple the 1.5 per cent of income
OL,14,Fthat goes on council tax for the
OL,15,Frichest households.
