OL,3,CCouncil tax burden almost doubles for
OL,4,Cpoorest households
OL,6,FThis comes at a time when council
OL,7,Ftaxes are expected to rise by the
OL,8,Fmaximum amount across almost every
OL,9,Fcounty in England, with the Government
OL,10,Fgiving permission for some to increase
OL,11,Frates further.
OL,13,FIn Scotland, last year's freeze on
OL,14,Fcouncil tax will end with rates
OL,15,Fexpected to rise across the country.
OL,17,FIn England and Scotland, council tax
OL,18,Fbands are set at 1991 property values.
OL,19,FThis is despite house prices rising at
OL,20,Fdifferent rates across the country.
