OL,6,FThe Government's calculations for
OL,7,Fcouncil spending power in England
OL,8,Fassume that rates are increased by the
OL,9,Fmaximum amount.
OL,11,FThe new Government funding settlement,
OL,12,Fannounced by Angela Rayner at the
OL,13,Fstart of February, sets total budgets
OL,14,Fat #64.2 billion.
