OL,6,FIn November 2024, the Government
OL,7,Fannounced the withdrawal of the Rural
OL,8,FService Delivery Grant which helped
OL,9,Fcover the increased cost of running
OL,10,Fservices in rural areas, such as local
OL,11,Fbuses.
OL,13,FAccording to analysis by the ITV
OL,14,FPeston programme, 42 of the councils
OL,15,Fwhich lost this funding received no
OL,16,Ffurther funding from the Recovery
OL,17,FGrant.
