OL,6,FThe County Council Network, which
OL,7,Frepresents 37 councils, say that four
OL,8,Fin five of their members are in a
OL,9,Fworse position than before the Autumn
OL,10,FBudget.
OL,12,FThey say that the additional costs
OL,13,Ffrom increases in National Living Wage
OL,14,Fand employer National Insurance, mean
OL,15,Fthat rural councils such as Devon are
OL,16,Flooking at a real-terms cut.
